column5: Hey guys, its been a while since ive been around the board.....anyways i thought i remembered a directory for cabins and camps that are available for rent.....im looking into a vacation this summer with a couple buddies and our girlfriends so it would have to be fairly cheap but then again i aint afraid to spend a little money and somewhere that we can rent a boat or something....anyways if there is a link i could access or if someone could just point me in the right direction would be much appreciated....thanks again guys.....feels good to be back btw
You might want to give a location or a couple locations.That may give you more feedback.
Here is the place for all of the info you will ever need. Brought to you by our fearless leader T.J.  Ontario Fishing   Art
This is a very useful tool.  The interactive map is great.  http://www.ontariooutfittersnetwork.com/
